Unitron:



Unitron fell back, but his wrists were still slowly being crusehd and 
grasped, and with deep wounds in his abdomen from the close up blasts by the 
'impostor', all Unitron could do was fire three optic blasts at Megatron's 
neck area, two at the top of his chest and one at the middle of the neck.
